%% Diagram: Diagram 5
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant E as CDN
    participant G as Gateway+Transform

    C->>E: GET /v1/.../w_800.webp
    E->>G: cache miss
    G->>G: parse + validate + lock
    alt cache MISS
        G->>G: fetch + libvips + store
    else derived found
        G->>G: serve cached
    end
    G-->>E: 200 + Cache-Control
    E-->>C: 200 (< 800ms)
